page.title: 10Ages and surnames in Seaton
page.content:
Of the 158 people in the Rutland village of Seaton, 27 were children below the age of 18. Of the adults, 4 are between 18 and 20 8 are between 20 and 25 38 are between 25 and 35 14 are between 35 and 45 22 are between 45 and 55 14 are between 55 and 65 25 are between 65 and 75 6 are over 75
The most common surnames were found to be Crowden (14), Watchorn (6) and Clarke (4), Turiccki (4), Johnson (4), Thompson (4).
Surnames unusual to this area were Berdinner, Gammel, Hobell, and Moat.
